  m_text: 'simply:


    - you are squid

    - squid is cool

    - try to get to
    the end of the level on the righthand side to collect the food

    - get there
    before the time limit ends and the blahaj eats the food

    - eat small fish
    for power ups (orange = fast, blue = slow, green = bigger, red = smaller)

    -
    do NOT eat pufferfish (they will inflate and kill you) or blahaj (this one shouldn''t
    have to be explained)'
